{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-20T13:43:03.328Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation structure refers to "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"how you interact with the model"},{"type":"text","text":": whether you ask everything in one go (single-turn) or build up through a dialogue (multi-turn). This is a critical distinction that affects reproducibility, cost, quality, and workflow design."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Single-Turn Prompting"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Definition"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Single-turn prompting"},{"type":"text","text":" means one prompt goes in, one response comes out. It's a complete, self-contained interaction with no context from previous exchanges."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Prompt: \"Classify this email into Billing, Bug, Feature, or Other.\"\nEmail: \"I was double charged this month.\"\nResponse: \"Category: Billing. Reason: The email is about incorrect charging.\""}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Key characteristics"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":"left"},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Attribute"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":"left"},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Single-Turn Value"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Reproducibility"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"High (same prompt, same output pattern)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Batch processing"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Yes (run 100 times automatically)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Consistency"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"High across runs"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Cost per piece"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Predictable"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Quality ceiling"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Limited by prompt quality"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Speed"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Fast (single API call)"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"When to use single-turn"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Single-turn is for production."},{"type":"text","text":" Use it when you need:"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Consistency"},{"type":"text","text":": \"If you produce 50 blog posts using a single-turn prompt, all 50 follow the same structure, voice, and quality level\""}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Reproducibility"},{"type":"text","text":": You need the same output every time with the same parameters"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Batch processing"},{"type":"text","text":": Automating 100+ runs without human intervention"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Simple tasks"},{"type":"text","text":": Quick lookups, information retrieval, simple commands"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Predictable costs"},{"type":"text","text":": You want to know exactly how much each response will cost"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Examples:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"What is the weather today?\""}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Classification tasks with clear rules"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Standardized reports (the same format every time)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"API calls in production pipelines"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Limitations"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Quality ceiling is limited by prompt quality"},{"type":"text","text":": You can't refine the output once it's generated. If the prompt is imperfect, the output is imperfect."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Multi-Turn Prompting"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Definition"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Multi-turn prompting"},{"type":"text","text":" is a conversation where you refine the output over several exchanges, adjusting direction with each response."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"It consists of "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"two or more sequential exchanges"},{"type":"text","text":" in which the meaning and appropriate response to each message depends on what was said in earlier turns."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Turn 1:\nUser: \"Give me a summary of climate change.\"\nAI: [provides summary]\n\nTurn 2:\nUser: \"Now give me examples.\"\nAI: [provides examples]\n\nTurn 3:\nUser: \"Now explain it to a 10-year-old.\"\nAI: [simplifies explanation]"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Key characteristics"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":"left"},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Attribute"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":"left"},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Multi-Turn Value"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Reproducibility"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Low (conversation path varies)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Batch processing"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"No (requires human in the loop)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Consistency"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Varied per conversation"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Cost per piece"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Varied (more turns = more tokens)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Quality ceiling"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Higher (human refinement in loop)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Speed"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Slow (multiple exchanges)"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"When to use multi-turn"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Multi-turn is for exploration."},{"type":"text","text":" Use it when you need:"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Exploration"},{"type":"text","text":": You're not sure what you want yet. You're exploring a topic, trying different angles, evaluating which approach resonates"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Complex refinement"},{"type":"text","text":": Adjustments are easier to describe in response to specific text than in advance"}]},{"type":"blockquote","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"This paragraph is too abstract. Replace the metaphor with a concrete example from manufacturing\" is a refinement you can only make after seeing the output."}]}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"One-off projects"},{"type":"text","text":": You're producing a single piece that won't be repeated, so investing in crystallizing a single-turn prompt isn't justified"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Creative work"},{"type":"text","text":": Direction emerges through collaboration"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Tasks too large or nuanced for a single prompt"},{"type":"text","text":": Breaking them into steps"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Examples:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Creative writing (iterating on drafts)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Code debugging (explaining errors, trying fixes)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Design feedback (reviewing, adjusting)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Research (exploring topics, asking follow-ups)"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"How it works"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Each turn adds to the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"conversation context"},{"type":"text","text":", allowing you to:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Build on previous responses"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Correct course"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Progressively refine the output"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The LLM sees the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"entire conversation history"},{"type":"text","text":" and can adjust based on your feedback."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Challenges"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"1. Conversation drift"},{"type":"text","text":": The exact sequence of refinements is difficult to reproduce, and the AI's behavior changes based on the full conversation history, not just the latest message."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"2. Cost"},{"type":"text","text":": As the conversation grows, the full history is sent with each new message, consuming tokens and increasing your API bill."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"3. State-tracking problem"},{"type":"text","text":": Managing a multi-turn conversation requires the AI system to solve what has been established, promised, or decided in earlier turns."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"The Best Workflow: Combine Both"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"The best workflow combines both modes:"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Start with multi-turn to explore and refine"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Then crystallize the result into single-turn for production"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Crystallization process"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"After a successful multi-turn conversation:"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Scroll back through the entire exchange"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Identify every instruction you gave across multiple turns"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"Make the opening more direct.\""}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"Remove the hedge in paragraph 3.\""}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"Use shorter sentences in the technical section.\""}]}]}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Combine all of them into a single prompt"},{"type":"text","text":" that produces the refined output on the first try"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Process:"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Take a piece of content you previously created through multi-turn conversation"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Analyze the conversation: what instructions did you give across multiple turns?"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"List every refinement"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Combine them into a single comprehensive prompt"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Test the single-turn version five times"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Does it produce equivalent quality? If not, identify what is missing and add it to the prompt"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Real-world examples"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example 1: Blog post creation (multi-turn → single-turn)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Multi-turn (exploration):"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Turn 1: User: \"Write a blog post about urban planning and AI.\"\nAI: [provides draft]\n\nTurn 2: User: \"Make the opening more direct.\"\nAI: [updates opening]\n\nTurn 3: User: \"Use shorter sentences in the technical section.\"\nAI: [simplifies]\n\nTurn 4: User: \"Remove the hedge in paragraph 3.\"\nAI: [removes hedging]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Crystallized single-turn (production):"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a blog post about urban planning and AI for city officials.\n\nRequirements:\n- Make the opening direct and specific\n- Use short sentences in the technical section (max 15 words)\n- Avoid hedging language (no \"might,\" \"could,\" \"possibly\")\n- 3 paragraphs total\n- Professional but friendly tone"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now you can produce 50 blog posts with the same structure, voice, and quality level."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example 2: Code debugging (multi-turn only)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Multi-turn (one-off project):"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Turn 1: User: \"I'm getting an error in this function.\"\nAI: [analyzes error]\n\nTurn 2: User: \"What's the likely cause?\"\nAI: [suggests fix]\n\nTurn 3: User: \"Try implementing that fix.\"\nAI: [provides corrected code]\n\nTurn 4: User: \"Now explain why it works.\"\nAI: [explains reasoning]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This is a one-off debugging session—you don't need to crystallize it into single-turn because you won't repeat this exact process."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example 3: Email classification (single-turn production)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Single-turn (production):"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Task: Classify this email into Billing, Bug, Feature, or Other.\n\nOutput JSON:\n{\n  \"category\": \"<one_of: Billing | Bug | Feature | Other>\",\n  \"reason\": \"<short explanation>\"\n}\n\nExamples:\nEmail: \"I was double charged.\"\n→ Category: Billing\nReason: The email is about incorrect charging.\n\nEmail: \"The app crashes.\"\n→ Category: Bug\nReason: A specific feature is crashing.\n\nNow classify this:\n\"I'd love a dark mode option.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This single-turn prompt will produce consistent results across 100+ emails."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Comparison table"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":"left"},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Aspect"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":"left"},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Single-Turn"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":"left"},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Multi-Turn"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Best for"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Production, batch processing"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Exploration, creative work"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Reproducibility"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"High"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Low"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Consistency"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"High across runs"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Varied per conversation"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Speed"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Fast (1 API call)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Slow (multiple exchanges)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Cost"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Predictable per piece"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Higher (full history sent each turn)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Quality ceiling"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Limited by prompt quality"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Higher (human refinement)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Batch processing"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Yes"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"No (requires human in loop)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Context needed"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Self-contained"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Builds on prior turns"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Key principle"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"The critical distinction is reproducibility."}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Single-turn prompt"},{"type":"text","text":": Produces the same output (approximately) every time you run it with the same parameters"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Multi-turn conversation"},{"type":"text","text":": Drifts. The exact sequence of refinements is difficult to reproduce, and the AI's behavior changes based on the full conversation history"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Summary"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Single-turn (production)"},{"type":"text","text":": One prompt → one response. High reproducibility, consistent quality, predictable cost. Best for standardized tasks and batch processing."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Multi-turn (exploration)"},{"type":"text","text":": Dialogue with multiple exchanges. Lower reproducibility, higher quality ceiling, variable cost. Best for creative work, complex refinement, and one-off projects."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Best workflow"},{"type":"text","text":": Start with multi-turn to explore and refine, then crystallize the result into a single-turn prompt for production."}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph"}]}}
